00:30:40.200 --> 00:30:41.320
what is that demonstrating?

494
00:30:41.320 --> 00:30:44.680
It's demonstrating that Jesus truly is king.

495
00:30:45.600 --> 00:30:47.240
We are part of his kingdom.

496
00:30:47.240 --> 00:30:50.440
It's showing that Christ reigns over all things.

497
00:30:50.800 --> 00:30:54.920
His reign is being revealed in the world when his church confesses him,

498
00:30:55.040 --> 00:30:58.240
his lordship and follows him as king.

499
00:30:58.920 --> 00:31:01.120
The church is an outpost of the kingdom.

