00:31:21.040 --> 00:31:24.280
And so you see Jesus lovingly laying down his life for his people.

507
00:31:24.280 --> 00:31:28.360
So as his people are now following the reign of the king, following his ways,

508
00:31:28.360 --> 00:31:32.880
while they're lovingly laying down their lives for one another, serving one another

