00:31:32.880 --> 00:31:35.360
in very practical ways.

510
00:31:35.360 --> 00:31:36.800
And they're bearing witness to the king.

511
00:31:36.800 --> 00:31:40.640
And as they're doing that, the Lord is adding to their number day by day.

512
00:31:43.080 --> 00:31:46.000
So sure, they're in the Roman Empire, but they are part of another kingdom.

513
00:31:46.360 --> 00:31:47.800
Jesus is the king.

514
00:31:47.800 --> 00:31:49.920
And the same is true for us where we're sat this morning.

