517
00:32:01.760 --> 00:32:05.320
to be part of God's community, to be part of his family,

518
00:32:06.000 --> 00:32:08.760
to know that he dwells with us

519
00:32:08.760 --> 00:32:11.760
and to be citizens of his glorious kingdom.

